cd service-pro-saas
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit"
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/servicepro.git
git push -u origin main
```

### **2. Deploy Backend - Railway (10 min)**
1. Go to https://railway.app
2. Login with GitHub
3. "New Project" → "Deploy from GitHub repo"
4. Settings → Root Directory: `backend`
5. Variables → Add all your API keys (Supabase, Twilio, Stripe, etc.)
6. Generate domain → Save the URL

### **3. Deploy Frontend - Vercel (10 min)**
1. Go to https://vercel.com
2. Login with GitHub
3. Import your repository
4. Root Directory: `frontend`
5. Environment Variables:
```
   NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-railway-url.railway.app
   NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...
